title: Part 2 with ‘The Bachelor’ Stylist and Makeup Artist
description:
In the second part of our exclusive interview with “Bachelor” stylist Cary Fetman and “Bachelor” makeup artist Gina Modica, the pair discuss how social media has changed the fashion of the show over the years.

Plus, Gina and Cary share how they got started in the industry and what it took to land their “dream jobs.”

Follow Cary @CaryFetman

Follow Gina @GinaModicaMakeup
